data.description: LOOKING FOR PRIVACY IN THE COUNTRY. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on 2.63 acres is located near Wentworth. All rooms are large. Huge Primary Bedroom suite with large bath that has a garden tub, double vanity and separate shower. Kitchen with island bar, pantry and lots of cabinets. Large den with fireplace. 2nd bedroom is almost as large as Primary Bedroom. Lots of privacy, nature and wildlife. You will love living in the country. Convenient to the entire county. Being sold in "AS IS" condition and priced at only $179,900. BEWARE OF DOGS, DON'T GET OUT OF CAR UNLESS YOU HAVE AN APPOINTMENT.
